## Code Style & Convention Compliance

- Follows Envoy repository conventions
- Uses existing logging patterns (ENVOY_LOG with debug level)
- Maintains thread-safety with proper mutex locking
- Consistent with existing error handling patterns
- No new dependencies introduced

## Metrics

